WEBVTT

00:00:14.068 --> 00:00:16.368
If humans could fly,

00:00:16.392 --> 00:00:17.819
without tools and machines,

00:00:17.843 --> 00:00:20.102
how fast do you think we would go?

00:00:20.126 --> 00:00:22.509
As of 2012, the world record

00:00:22.533 --> 00:00:24.606
for fastest short-distance sprint speed

00:00:24.630 --> 00:00:27.339
is roughly 27 miles per hour.

00:00:27.363 --> 00:00:29.236
Running speed depends on how much force

00:00:29.260 --> 00:00:31.114
is exerted by the runner's legs,